0.0.0 - 21.07.15
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Added bitwise instructions.
* Added modulo instruction.
* Added functionality for optional arguments.
* Redesigned memory structure.


0.0.1 - 31.07.15
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Added labels.
* Made some modifications to how unsigned 32 bit integers were stored internally and fixed a bug
where operations beyond the bounds of 32 bit signed integers caused an error.
* Added jump-to-subroutine instruction, JSR, which can be used for delegating instructions.
* Implemented better line comments as well as block comments.
* Implemented stack memory.
* Implemented ability to retrieve information from hardware.